        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Call us or fill out our contact form. We'll set up a no-cost, no-obligation screening at a time that works for you.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div style="text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
        <div style="width: 96px; height: 96px; margin: 0 auto 1rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9e8 0%, #ddf0cc 100%); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 2.5rem; border: 3px solid var(--green); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(139,195,74,0.2);">🔍</div>
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">2. We Review Needs & Insurance</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">Our team evaluates your child's needs, verifies your insurance benefits, and builds a personalized care plan — all at no cost to you.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div style="text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
        <div style="width: 96px; height: 96px; margin: 0 auto 1rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef5e7 0%, #fbe8c8 100%); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 2.5rem; border: 3px solid var(--orange); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245,166,35,0.2);">🌟</div>
